 For indides\nof heavy-lanthanide elements, the Cd-tracer remains on the In-sublattice and\nrelaxation gives the diffusional jump-frequency.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 May 2018 20:14:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-10"}
