itable for water splitting, where CN and SiAs are\nfavorable at all pH values. Structures with quartic band edges are expected to\nbe efficient for thermoelectric applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 May 2018 20:42:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-01"}
