rates the KdV\nhierarchy, and its orbits are the Schubert cells of the restricted\nGrassmannian.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 May 2018 21:21:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 14 Nov 2019 13:35:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-28"}
