\nrepresent impact fragments ejected from previous collisions. Outer belt Vp\nasteroids exhibit disparate spectral, mineralogic, and meteorite analog\ncharacteristics and likely originate from diverse parent bodies. The discovery\nof two additional likely basaltic asteroids provides additional evidence for an\nouter-belt basaltic asteroid population.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 May 2018 23:08:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-27"}
