se models. Considering the success of free random variables theory in a wide\nvariety of disciplines, we hope that the results presented here foster the\nadditional application of these ideas in the area of brain sciences.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 May 2018 15:40:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 15 Nov 2020 17:44:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-17"}
