e carried out at the experiment that will detect supernova\nneutrinos and will measure precisely solar neutrino oscillation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 May 2018 14:24:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 28 Nov 2018 18:17:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-30"}
